title: Doctor Who Files Disc 1 - snuggles79
description:
This is an ISO file of Disc 1 of the UK Partwork "Doctor Who Files". It has been encoded as region free.

This DVD features the first two Christopher Eccleston Doctor stories - "Rose" and "The End Of The World".

Doctor - Christopher Eccleston
Rose (Assistant) - Billie Piper

Episode 1.1 - "Rose" - Is someone trying to take over Britain's shops?
Episode 1.2 - "The End Of The World" - Earth death in five minutes ...

Rated: PG
